14
00:01:20.219 --> 00:01:23.555
<i>but the twins were unscathed.</i>

15
00:01:23.639 --> 00:01:27.726
<i>Samaritan grew to fight for justice.
to be a protector.</i>

16
00:01:30.145 --> 00:01:33.357
<i>Nemesis. consumed by revenge.</i>

17
00:01:33.440 --> 00:01:36.151
