as his parents had.</i>

18
00:01:37.778 --> 00:01:41.156
<i>Samaritan tried to contain
his brother's fury.</i>

19
00:01:41.240 --> 00:01:44.117
<i>so Nemesis forged a powerful weapon.</i>

20
00:01:44.201 --> 00:01:48.664
<i>A hammer that he poured
all his hate and rage into.</i>

21
00:01:48.747 --> 00:01:52.125
<i>It was the only thing
that could destroy Samaritan.</i>

22
00:01:53.460 --> 00:01:56.255
<i>Nemesis lured him to the power plant.</i>

23
00:01:58.507 --> 00:02:01.718
